@startuml activity-log-usage
title Activity - Log inventory usage (Release 1.0)
|Operational Staff / Browser|
start
:Open Log Usage page;
:Click Submit Usage;
:Select item, quantity, date (YYYY-MM-DD);
|UI validation|
if (Item selected, qty > 0, date not future?) then (no)
  :Show inline / banner error;
  stop
endif
|System (React)|
:POST /api/inventory/usage\n{itemId, quantityUsed, usageDate};
|Express + Mongoose|
if (Valid itemId, qty, date format?) then (no)
  :400 JSON error message;
  |Operational Staff / Browser|
  :Show error;
  stop
endif
if (quantityUsed <= currentStock?) then (no)
  :400: cannot exceed stock;
  |Operational Staff / Browser|
  :Show error;
  stop
endif
:Decrement currentStock, bump totalUsed;
:Recalc consumption rate and risk;
:Save **Inventory** document;
:Create **UsageLog** with remainingStock;
:200 JSON { item, log };
|Operational Staff / Browser|
:Refresh lists; show success;
stop

@enduml
